text: Destiny (, translit. al-Maṣīr; ) is a 1997 Egyptian French drama movie directed by Youssef Chahine and starring Nour El-Sherif, Laila Eloui, Mahmoud Hemida, Safia El Emari, Mohamed Mounir, Khaled El Nabawy. ==Other websites== * Category:1997 drama movies Category:Egyptian movies Category:French drama movies Category:Movies directed by Youssef Chahine
title: Destiny (1997 movie)
